# Dialogue Designer — Build & Deploy

When ANY `.lua` file under `memories/DialogueEngine/Designer/` is modified, you MUST run the build script and copy the output to the Roblox Studio plugins folder before finishing:

```powershell
node build-rbxmx.cjs
Copy-Item "DialogueDesigner.rbxmx" "$env:LOCALAPPDATA\Roblox\Plugins\DialogueDesigner.rbxmx" -Force
```

Both commands run from `memories/DialogueEngine/Designer/`.

This rebuilds the `.rbxmx` plugin bundle and deploys it so Studio picks up changes on next restart/reload.
